<sect1 id="md__docs_rest-directives_1autotoc_md87">
<title>tabs</title>
<para>:link: see <ulink url="https://docs.typo3.org/m/typo3/docs-how-to-document/main/en-us/WritingReST/CheatSheet.html#tabs">tabs in reST</ulink></para>
